\newlabel{fig:ragale_enforcer}{{3}{19}{Ragale Symbolic Enforcer. Compared to the Dvipada pipeline (Figure~\ref {fig:enforcer}), Yati NFA is removed and the Ga\d {n}a NFA uses 22 states (2 patterns) instead of 69 (8 patterns). The FST pipeline is identical except for Kannada Unicode codepoints}{figure.caption.55}{}}
